## What this covers

- The GLB model files served by the widget (`assets/glb/*.glb`, hosted on Supabase).
- `assets/parts-catalog.json` — the catalogue of named structures derived from the
  Z-Anatomy model (node names, Latin/English nomenclature, systems, laterality).
- `assets/parts-neighbors.json` — nearest-neighbour relationships computed from the
  geometry of those models.

