## Changes made (indicated per CC BY-SA 4.0 §3(a)(1)(B))

The Z-Anatomy source was modified for this project. Notably:

- Only subsets of structures are extracted and shown ("region isolation"); no whole
  body system is rendered.
- The models were re-exported to glTF/GLB and **meshopt-compressed** for streaming.
- Vessels and nerves were re-exported directly from the Z-Anatomy `Startup.blend` to
  preserve their thin curve geometry.
- A validated catalogue and nearest-neighbour dataset were generated from the models.

